title: Person With Headscarf Medium Skin Tone
description: A person wearing a headscarf, shown with a medium skin tone. This emoji can represent religious observance, cultural attire, or a fashion choice.

Its rounded features and a serene expression convey a sense of modesty and cultural identity, making it a thoughtful way to represent individuals or express respect and understanding in digital conversations on Apple devices.
